com.igeekinc.util.fileinfo

Class FileGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.igeekinc.util.fileinfo.TreeInfoBase
      • com.igeekinc.util.fileinfo.FileGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class FileGroup
extends TreeInfoBase
    A FileGroup identifies the "group" a file should be placed in. For example, Microsoft Office documents could be classed as a group. The FileGroup is a hierarchy and should be based on the reverse DNS of the manufacturer.
